Firefox(Android) (Firefox (Android))

Go to the three-dot menu and select Settings > Privacy > Cookies.
You get three choices: Enabled, Enabled Excluding 3rd Party, or Disabled. 
To erase all cookies, on the Privacy screen, check the box by Clear Private Data on Exit. 
